* DONE
** Added preference: extensions.lyz.use_utf8
  - by default all characters are escaped
  - set extensions.lyz.use_utf8 to true in about:config to avoid escaping
** Added support for non-latin scripts
  - tested on simplified Chinese
  - set extensions.lyz.use_utf8 to true in about:config to avoid escaping
  - cite key will use numeric value of the unicode characters, e.g.         9648 instead of 陈. Only the first character from author name is used. Title is not used, only year.

